          <p><b><i>I have read the de minimis assessment and I am satisfied that it represents a fair and proportionate assessment of the impact of the measure.</i></b></p>
        </content>
      </level>
      <level>
        <content>
          <p>Signed:  <b><i>John Glen</i></b><marker name="tab" /><marker name="tab" /><marker name="tab" /><marker name="tab" /><marker name="tab" />Date: 19/03/2020</p>
        </content>
      </level>
      <level>
        <content>
          <p><b>Further information sheet</b></p>
        </content>
      </level>
      <level>
        <content>
          <p>Please provide additional evidence in subsequent sheets, as required. </p>
        </content>
      </level>
